speciality.name: Spine Surgeon
speciality.description: Spine surgery is a specialized branch of orthopedic surgery. Mainly focuses on treating spine and vertibal column related diseases. Orthopedic surgeons that undergoe advance training in spine are called spine surgeons
speciality.conditions: Microscopic dissectomy,Endoscopic dissectomy,Spine fusion procedure,Minimally invasive spine surgery,Cervical & dorsal myelopathy,Scoliosis,Kyphosis,Spine tumors,Spine injuries & trauma,Posture correction
